Package hu.klenium.tetris

Enum UserCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UserCommand>
      • hu.klenium.tetris.UserCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UserCommand>
    public enum UserCommand
extends java.lang.Enum<UserCommand>
    A command is an event type, caused by the game's player to control the falling tetromino.
    TetrisGame recieves only an UserCommand, so that it does not depend on the input type (eg. key names, button types).

    • Enum Constant Summary
